      <h2 class="project__intro__opening font--regular">
        Can we help elect the President?
      </h2>
      <p class="project__intro__body">
        We had one goal; help make Hillary Clinton the 45<sup>th</sup> President 
        of the United States of America. You know how that ended. What you might 
        not know about is the tireless work of a small team of technologists 
        who dedicated themselves to the <abbr title="Hillary for America">HFA</abbr> campaign. 
        You don’t know about that because that’s how we designed it.
        From the beginning, our mantra was, “don’t be the story.”
      </p>
      <p class="project__intro__extended project__shout">
