  <div class="g-main__item project__body">
    <h3>Blocks</h3>
    <p>
      The Groundwork Blocks were highly configurable drop-in widgets for collecting
      payments and email subscriptions. We built them to allow our customers
      a way to quickly implement donation collections and email subscriptions
      with little to no engineering resources. With a single <code>div</code>
      and a <code>script</code> tag, customers had full access to our APIs.
    </p>
